name: Worksheets
descriptionHtml:
### Endpoint for creating new worksheet

Request payload must contain the following fields:

course_module_id: STRING,
topic_type_id: STRING,
topic_type: STRING,
title: STRING

Request:

POST - https://apiqa.inquitech.in/api/v1/worksheets

raw 
  {
    "course_module_id": "1",
    "topic_type_id": "1",
    "topic_type":"VIDEO",
    "title":"Video 1"
}

Response:

400 - Bad Request 

  {"status":400,"status_type":"error","message":"notNull Violation: worksheet.attachments cannot be null","count":null,"data":null}
